# VMS Deposit Discovery AI — Phase 1: Python ML Pipeline

## Background

The interactive dashboard (proof-of-concept with simulated data) is complete and live at GitHub Pages. The roadmap's next active step is building the **real Python ML pipeline** — downloading open-access geoscience data, engineering features, training the classifier, and producing a genuine prospectivity map of the Bathurst Mining Camp.

This plan covers **Phase 1: Data Preparation** and sets up the full project scaffold for subsequent phases.

